sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant Client as Browser / REST client
    participant API as Express server
    participant FS as File system
    participant A3P as a3p-parser
    participant VM as tweedle-vm
    participant Evidence as evidence files

    Student->>Client: choose project
    Client->>API: POST /api/launch { project }
    API->>FS: read .a3p bytes
    FS-->>API: bytes
    API->>A3P: parseA3P(bytes)
    A3P-->>API: AliceProject
    API-->>Client: launched + projectName

    Student->>Client: edit procedure marker
    Client->>API: POST /api/code/edit-procedure
    API->>API: mutate state.procedures
    API->>Evidence: write edited-project + proof JSON
    Evidence-->>API: artifact paths
    API-->>Client: proved

    Student->>Client: run world
    Client->>API: POST /api/world/run
    API->>VM: executeProject(parsedProject)
    VM-->>API: execution_log
    API->>Evidence: write run-world-result.json
    API-->>Client: completed + evidence

    Student->>Client: save project
    Client->>API: POST /api/project/save
    API->>FS: copy source or write placeholder .a3p
    API->>Evidence: write desktop-save-operation-result.json
    API-->>Client: saved
